    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis, <date>anno domini nostri Iesu
                            Christi millesimo centesimo septuagesimo sexto, regnante
                                <persName>Frederico</persName> dei gratia Romanorum
                                <rs>imperatore</rs> et semper augusto, quarto ydus martii,
                            indictione VIIII</date>, exemplar antiqui instrumenti factum. In nomine
                        sancte et individue Trinitatis. <date>Anno ab incarnatione eiusdem domini
                            nostri Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo octavo, sextodecimo kalendarum
                            octubris, indictione prima</date>, et ideo in dei nomine ego quidem
                        domina <persName>Matilda</persName>, inclita <rs>comitissa</rs>, filia donni
                            <persName>Bonifatii</persName>
                        <rs>marchionis</rs>, per cartulam precariam atque <rs>emphyteotecariam</rs>
                        iuris nomine concedo vobis <persName><name>Yldebrando</name></persName>
                        iugera duo; et <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Ogizone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Yldebrando</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                            <persName>Sigezo</persName> et <persName><name>Uberto</name></persName>
                        germani iugera duo; <persName><name>Aczo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Sigezo</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Alfredum</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Albertus</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Martinus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Gregorio</name></persName> iugero duo;
                                <persName><name>Lanbertus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Bonardo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de <rs>presbitero</rs>
                        <persName><name>Ugo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Petrus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Severo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> germani et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Albareto</placeName> de
                            <persName><name>Roczo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Restano</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Leo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Maginardo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de <placeName>Sancto
                            Iohanne</placeName> iugera duo;
                            <persName><name>Martinus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Aczo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Omizo</name></persName> iugerum unum;
                                <persName><name>Ugo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Raginbaldo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Lamberto</name></persName> iugerum unum;
                                <persName><name>Alberto Candido</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Gaiule</placeName>, <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName>
                        et <persName><name>Iohanne</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs>nepos</rs> eorum iugera duo; <persName><name>Petrus</name></persName>
                        filius <persName><name>Petri</name></persName> faber et
                                <persName><name>Andrea Stanperto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> de presbitero
                                <persName><name>Leo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> faber et
                                <persName><name>Martino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Leo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> nepos eorum iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Bonando</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Steuuzo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Beneventano</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Andrea</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Pregite</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Vitale</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Iohanne</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Gotolo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Savorecto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Pregite</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Bononio</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Leo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Sicardo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Marco</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Iohanne</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Ragiberto</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Formigine</placeName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Ermengarda</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Petrus Suxinaro</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> canauaro iugerum unum;
                                <persName><name>Bonellus</name></persName> bovulcus iurerum unum;
                                <persName><name>Rodulfus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Engelbertus</name></persName> unum,
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Fontana</placeName> et
                            <persName><name>Petrus</name></persName> et <persName><name>Alberto
                                Prilingarde</name></persName> II,
                            <persName><name>Stefanus</name></persName>
                        <rs>diaconus</rs> et <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Everardo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Bonvisino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> iugera duo,
                                <persName><name>Arduino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Ugo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Teuzo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Lanfranco</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Rodaldo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani de
                            <placeName>Nugareto</placeName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Ragimundo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Leo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Giberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Lamberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Bernardo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Gontardo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guarino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Gandulfo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Ioannino</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani et
                                <persName><name>Dagiberto</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Petrus Longobardus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> montario et
                                <persName><name>Girardo Pavanese</name></persName> iugera duo,
                                <persName><name>Goctefredo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Amacza</name></persName> villano iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Blanco</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Azo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Girardus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Stefanus</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                        namque <persName><name>Rollando</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Aco</name></persName> in tertiam portionem de duo
                        iugera, <persName><name>Ingezoni</name></persName> aliam tertiam, sitque
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Teuzoni</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Stefano</name></persName> in tertiam;
                                <persName><name>Iohannes Favaro</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Andrea</name></persName> in tertiam partem de duobus
                        iugera et <persName><name>Gregorius</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Ildebrando</name></persName> in duabus partibus;
                        scilicet in vos et in vestris heredibus usque in perpetuum. Que autem iam
                        dicta iugera sunt in <rs>curte</rs>
                        <placeName><geogName>Celula</geogName></placeName>, quorum vocabula sunt
                        curte de <geogName><placeName>Paulecla</placeName></geogName> et curte de
                                <placeName><geogName>Radigosa</geogName></placeName>, et in curte
                                <geogName><placeName>Gisso</placeName></geogName> et in aliis locis,
                        ubicumque nunc date sunt vel inantea date erunt tantummodo ad habendum,
                        tenendum, fruendum, fatiendum, quicquid vobis utile erit, eo videlicet modo,
                        ut <rs>roccam</rs> de <placeName>Gissadello</placeName>, pro qua hec omnia
                        do vobis, ab hac ora inantea incastellare, guitare et laborare et claudere
                        debetis, sicut decet et conveniens erit, ita ut omni anno de mense martio
                        denariorum Veneticorum persolvere debeatis per unumquemque iugerum ad
                                <orgName><placeName>ecclesiam sancti Silvestri</placeName></orgName>
                        usque in perpetuum. Si vero predicta rocca permanserit et si domina Matilda
                        in aliquo modo eam reliquerit vel vastaverit sine ulla occasione, que fieri
                        potest, predictam cartulam deinceps permaneat usque in perpetuum. Et
                        promitto ego domina predicta Matilda tam pro me quam pro meos successores
                        vobis supradictis petitoris vel vestris heredibus usque in perpetuo
                        defensare auctorizare. Si qua vero pars, qui contra hanc paginam
                        emphyteotecaria ire temptaverint et non observaverint omnia, quod superius
                        legitur, tunc componat illa pars, qui hoc non observaverint, ad partem fidem
                        servantem pene nomine solidi centum denariorum Lucensium, et post penam
                        solutam cartulam precariam maneat in sua firmitate. Actum in loco
                            <placeName>sancti Cesarii</placeName>. Supra legitur: Matilda dei
                        gratia, si quid est, subscripsi. Ego
                            <persName><name>Daniel</name></persName>
                        <placeName>Montebelliensis</placeName>
                        <rs>archipresbiter</rs> interfui. <persName><name>Ubaldo</name></persName>
                        de <placeName>Scoveto</placeName> et +
                            <persName><name>Ugizone</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name>Ragineri</name></persName>.
                                <persName><name>Gandulfo</name></persName> da
                            <placeName>Broilo</placeName> namque +
                            <persName><name>Rodulfo</name></persName> de <placeName>Monte
                            Claro</placeName> rogati sunt. Ego
                            <persName><name>Conon</name></persName> subscripsi et fieri rogavi. Ego
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> dictus <rs>prior</rs>
                        vidi et scripsi. In dei nomine, ego <persName><name>Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Tabellio">tabellio</rs> hanc cartulam precariam, sicut
                        superius legitur, scripsi et complevi. Dominus
                                <persName><name>Nicholaus</name></persName> et dominus
                                <persName><name>Zaccarus</name></persName>
                        <rs>iudices</rs> de <rs>comuni</rs>
                        <geogName><placeName>Bononie</placeName></geogName>,
                                <persName><name>Pegoloctus</name></persName>
                        <rs>causidicus</rs>, <persName><name>Ardicono</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Rainerius</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Aldizone</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Zuccherus</name></persName> ad hanc cartam antiquam
                        et novam audiendam interfuere et huius rei causa testes vocati sunt. Ego
                            <persName key="#Copyist #Notary"><name>Ugo</name></persName> dei gratia
                        comunis Bononie <rs>notarius</rs> hoc presens instrumentum, ut vidi in
                        antiquo, subscripsi et firmavi.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
